('tt9848626', 'Hotel Transylvania: Transformania', NULL, 2021, NULL, 'movie', 'United States', 'Drac\'s Pack is back, like you\'ve never seen them before in the final chapter of \'Hotel Transylvania\'.', 'When Van Helsing\'s mysterious invention, the \"Monsterfication Ray\", goes haywire, Drac and his monster pals are all transformed into humans, and Johnny becomes a monster. In their new mismatched bodies, Drac, stripped of his powers, and an exuberant Johnny, loving life as a monster, must team up and race across the globe to find a cure before it\'s too late, and before they drive each other crazy. With help from Mavis and the hilariously human Drac Pack, the heat is on to find a way to switch themselves back before their transformations become permanent. —Sony Pictures', 'Adventure,Animation,Comedy', 0, '[\'Brian Hull\', \'Andy Samberg\', \'Selena Gomez\', \'Kathryn Hahn\', \'Steve Buscemi\', \'David Spade\', \'Keegan-Michael Key\', \'Asher Blinkoff\', \'Brad Abrell\', \'Fran Drescher\', \'Jim Gaffigan\', \'Molly Shannon\', \'Chloé Malaisé\']', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTVhMmI2OTUtYTIzNC00NDAwLTg4OTEtMjA5YzdmNGNkMjlhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODk4OTc3MTY@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg'),
